fields.description:
In HPE Singapore demo cloud we have installed Euca 4.2.1

The setup is following

1 host - CLC
1 host - UFS / Console / Walrus
1 host - CC / SC
2 hosts - NC

We are not able to login to the console. It keeps timing out. The log suggest console is unable to establish HTTPS connection with the UFS. We are not sure how to fix the problem.

The installation is a fresh install. 

